### Security Features
- Password hashing
- Session-based authentication
- Login protection using @login_required
- CSRF protection with Flask-WTF
- Secure file upload handling for payment proofs

### Testing Strategy
- Manual testing of authentication flows
- Validation of payout order generation
- Payment tracking verification
- User acceptance testing with savings group participants